  <bioghist id="aspace_7b0317cc5196d4c55fec29207d14cbbc">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Henry J. Howe enlisted on Aug. 24, 1861 at Vesper, N.Y., mustered in as a private, Oneida Independent company, Cavalry in September of 1861. He served three years and mustered out in September of 1864.</p>  </bioghist>
